OL,3,CNew water saving labels 'waste of time
OL,4,Cand money', critics tell ITV News
OL,6,FThe new labels will be comparable to
OL,7,Fthe existing energy labels on
OL,8,Fproducts, but may prove to be more
OL,9,Fcontroversial, as ITV News' Consumer
OL,10,FEditor Chris Choi reports
OL,12,FNew compulsory water efficiency labels
OL,13,Fare set to be unveiled by the UK
OL,14,Fgovernment, the details of which ITV
OL,15,FNews can reveal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
