PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776957068
OL,3,CNew water saving labels 'waste of time
OL,4,Cand money', critics tell ITV News
OL,6,FThe labels will rate household
OL,7,Fappliances like showers, dishwashers,
OL,8,Ftaps, washing machines and toilets.
OL,9,FThey'll be comparable to the existing
OL,10,Fenergy labels on products, but may
OL,11,Fprove to be more controversial.
OL,13,FAlthough the labels are designed to
OL,14,Fprevent water waste, some industry
OL,15,Finsiders say that these labels are a
OL,16,Fwaste of time and money.
OL,18,FThe government's Water Minister Emma
OL,19,FHardy, who introduced the labels, told
OL,20,FITV News: "The reason why people save
OL,21,Fmoney is for two reasons.
OL,26,@|D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776957068
OL,3,CNew water saving labels 'waste of time
OL,4,Cand money', critics tell ITV News
OL,6,F"One ,they use less water, and two,
OL,7,Fthey're using less energy to heat that
OL,8,Fwater, because 11% of peoples' energy
OL,9,Fbills are actually because of the cost
OL,10,Fof heating water."
OL,12,FBut not everyone in the building trade
OL,13,Fis convinced. The Builders Merchants
OL,14,FFederation agrees with the principle
OL,15,Fof encouraging more effective water
OL,16,Fuse - but claims that this solution is
OL,17,Ffar from efficient.
OL,26,@rD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776957068
OL,3,CNew water saving labels 'waste of time
OL,4,Cand money', critics tell ITV News
OL,6,F"There was a water label that already
OL,7,Fexisted and then of course the
OL,8,Fgovernment decided to introduce a new
OL,9,Fwater label," the Federation's Chief
OL,10,FExecutive John Newcombe told ITV News.
OL,12,F"It causes confusion among consumers
OL,13,Fand confusion amongst the
OL,14,Fmanufacturers themselves."
OL,16,FThe government says the big difference
OL,17,Fis that the old labels were part of a
OL,18,Fvoluntary system, so take-up could not
OL,19,Fbe enforced.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
